{"article_id":"MiJWurrBgWJ7xEMb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US President Donald Trump has issued an angry response","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"after a TV interview on Sunday alleged","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"that officials had held discussions","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"to have him removed .","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"Mr Trump tweeted of `` illegal and treasonous '' behaviour and an `` illegal coup attempt '' .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"In the interview , ex-acting FBI chief Andrew McCabe said","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"talks had been held in 2017","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"about invoking a clause","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that can remove a president","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"deemed unfit .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"The Senate Judiciary Committee chairman has vowed to investigate the claims .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Lindsey Graham said","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"the claims were an `` attempted bureaucratic coup '' .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Mr McCabe said","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein had held discussions on the number of cabinet members and others","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"needed to invoke the clause , the 25th Amendment of the US Constitution .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"In a series of tweets on Monday morning , he condemned `` so many lies by now disgraced acting FBI Director Andrew McCabe .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"He was fired for lying","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"and now his story gets even more deranged .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"`` He and Rod Rosenstein ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"who was hired by","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"[ then Attorney General ] Jeff Sessions","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"( another beauty ) ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"look like they were planning a very illegal act ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"and got caught . ''","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Mr Trump added :","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"`` There is a lot of explaining","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"to do to the millions of people","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"who had just elected a president","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"who they really like","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"and who has done a great job for them with the military .","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"Vets .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"Economy and so much more .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"This was the illegal and treasonous 'insurance policy ' in full action ! ''","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"The president quoted a comment on the Fox and Friends programme","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"this was `` an illegal coup attempt '' ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"adding `` True ! ''","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"The White House said","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"Mr McCabe ,","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"who was fired last year","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"for allegedly lying to government investigators ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"had `` no credibility '' .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"The justice department said","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Mr McCabe 's account was `` inaccurate and factually incorrect '' .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"Allegations","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"that Mr Rosenstein discussed invoking the 25th Amendment","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"were first reported last year by the New York Times .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"However , Mr McCabe 's quotes are the first","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"to be made on the record from someone present at the meeting","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"where the alleged comments were reportedly made -","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"in May 2017 ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"after Mr Trump fired FBI director James Comey .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"`` The discussion of the 25th Amendment was simply","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"[ that ]","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Rod raised the issue","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"and discussed it with me in the context","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"of thinking about how many other cabinet officials might support such an effort , ''","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Mr McCabe also said","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"Mr Rosenstein was openly `` counting votes , or possible votes ''","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"and that he was `` very concerned '' about the president `` his capacity and about his intent at that point in time . '' `` To be fair ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"it was an unbelievably stressful time ...","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"it was really something","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"that he kind of threw out in a very frenzied chaotic conversation . ''","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Mr Rosenstein has previously strongly denied having such discussions ,","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"there was `` no basis ''","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"to invoking the amendment .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"In the 60 Minutes interview ,","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"aired on Sunday ,","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"Mr McCabe also covered allegations","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"Mr Rosenstein had offered to secretly record Mr Trump , amid concerns about possible obstruction of justice","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"relating to the investigation into alleged collusion between the president 's campaign team and Russia .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"When the allegations first emerged in the New York Times ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Mr Rosenstein said","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"the report was `` inaccurate and factually incorrect '' .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"A source told the BBC at the time","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"that Mr Rosenstein 's comment `` was sarcastic","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"and was never discussed with any intention","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"of recording a conversation with the president '' .","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"However , Mr McCabe said","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"that Mr Rosenstein `` was not joking .","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"He was absolutely serious '' .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"`` It was incredibly turbulent , incredibly stressful .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"And it was clear to me that that stress was - was impacting the deputy attorney general . ''","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"He added :","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"`` I never actually considered taking him up on the offer . ''","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"He described Mr McCabe 's comments as `` stunning ''","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"and pledged to hold a hearing at the Senate Judiciary Committee","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"to determine `` who 's telling the truth '' .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"H said","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"he could issue subpoenas","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"- a court order","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"forcing a witness to appear","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"to give testimony -","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"`` if that 's what it takes '' .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"It is one way","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"that provides for the removal of a president ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"if he or she is `` unable to discharge the powers and duties of office '' .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"What this exactly means is open to interpretation .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"The majority of the president 's cabinet plus the vice-president would need to sign a letter .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"The vice-president would then become acting president .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"The president can give a written response","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"then Congress would have to decide on removal ,","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"requiring a two-thirds majority in both houses .","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"Ronald Reagan and George W Bush used the amendment","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"to temporarily transfer power","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"when they were medically anaesthetised .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"He took over as acting director of the FBI in 2017","depth":4},{"id":110,"text":"and was himself fired as deputy director in March last year","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"just two days before he was due to retire .","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"He was sacked by Jeff Sessions ,","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"who said","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"an internal review had found","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"he leaked information","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"and misled investigators .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"Mr McCabe denied the claims","depth":4},{"id":118,"text":"and said","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"he was being targeted","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"because of his involvement in the Russian collusion inquiry .","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"He has now written a book on his time in his posts .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":243,"left":230,"right":242,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":230,"left":159,"right":229,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":137,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":134,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":126,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":0,"right":124,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":1,"right":123,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":130,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":5,"right":129,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":129,"left":6,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":7,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":10,"right":131,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":131,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},